                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-217-off1126 t18240603-217-cd1127"></join>, six quarts of brandy, value 20 s.; and two quarts of Geneva, value 10 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18240603-217-victim1855" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t18240603-217-viclabel1128" type="occupation">our Lord the King</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-217-victim1855 t18240603-217-viclabel1128"></join>
